          <title>Goggia wins to lock up World Cup super-G title. Aicher further closes gap on overall leader Shiffrin</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Sofia Goggia has won her third super-G of the season at the World Cup finals to secure the discipline title and Emma Aicher further closed the gap to overall leader Mikaela Shiffrin.]]></description>
