        <item>
          <title>Lendeborg scores 25, and Midwest's top-seeded Michigan rolls to a 95-72 win over Saint Louis</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Yaxel Lendeborg punctuated his 25-point outing with a massive dunk in transition, and the Midwest Region’s top-seeded Michigan advanced to the Sweet 16 with a 95-72 win over Saint Louis in the second round of the NCAA Tournament.]]></description>
